milestones.description: Rajin Saleh and Alok Kapali's 128-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 108 between Athar Ali Khan and Faruque Ahmed
Inzamam-ul-Haq has broken the record for most catches (91) in ODIs for PAK, going past Ijaz Ahmed's 90
This is the highest match aggregate (546) involving teams Pakistan & Bangladesh in ODIs

stories.title: Pakistan ease to 58-run win to wrap series 5-0
stories.summary: Pakistan coasted to a comfortable 58-run victory in the last match of their one-day international series against Bangladesh to complete a 5-0 drubbing
